project.name: protohx
project.description: Protohx is cross-platform haxe implementation of "Google Protocol Buffers". This is Haxe port of ActionScript3 protoc plugin "protoc-gen-as3". Protobuf sites: https://code.google.com/p/protobuf/ https://code.google.com/p/protoc-gen-as3/ Protohx project urls: https://github.com/nitrobin/protohx https://bitbucket.org/nitrobin/protohx
project.version: First release, basic features is working correctly
